ReviewText: Last month I bought two jars of Alta Rica with the new jar design and label. What a disappointment – little wonder they were on special offer. The coffee tastes cheap and muddy and not at all like the Alta Rica I've been drinking and enjoying for many years. I notice that Nescafe/Nestle are saying that the formulation hasn't changed.  Fortunately, I tend to stock up on coffee and so still have some jars of the previous design and label in the cupboard. Doing a like-for-like test, I find it difficult to take seriously the assertion that only the jar/label has changed and so have ceased to buy Alta Rica and will look for an alternative. In the meantime, my older stocks will keep me going for another month.
